title: Heartwarming twist after Aussie lost $100,000 Nissan Patrol she won in online charity raffle
description: A young Australian woman who won her dream car in a charity raffle before it was later repossessed has had some good news.

title: SIMON JORDAN: BBC should BOOT OUT lemmings who went on strike for Gary Lineker
description: SIMON JORDAN: Once the virtue-signalling Alan Shearer, Ian Wright and Mark Chapman refused to appear on the BBC last weekend, a herd mentality ensued and they all had to follow.

title: Whoopi Goldberg issues public apology for using the word 'gypped'
description: Whoopi Goldberg has apologized after making an obscene racial slur on The View on Wednesday when she used the term 'gypped' while speaking about Trump and Stormy Daniels alleged affair.

title: Jeremy Hunt gave assured performance with reforms to childcare and pensions. Will it turn the tide?
description: Unveiling a £21billion package to boost growth,  Chancellor Jeremy Hunt declared the UK economy had a 'future of enormous potential'.
